Lemma Zdiv_mul_pos: forall m l, l >= 0 -> two_p (N+l) <= m * d <= two_p (N+l) + two_p l -> forall n, 0 <= n < two_p N -> Z.div n d = Z.div (m * n) (two_p (N + l)).
intros m l l_pos [LO HI] n RANGE.
assert ((m * n - two_p (N + l) * q) * d = k * n + two_p (N + l) * r).
assert (k * n <= two_p (N + l) - two_p l).
replace (N + l) with (l + N) by omega.
replace (two_p l * two_p N - two_p l) with (two_p l * (two_p N - 1)) by ring.
assert (two_p (N + l) * r <= two_p (N + l) * d - two_p (N + l)).
replace (two_p (N + l) * d - two_p (N + l)) with (two_p (N + l) * (d - 1)) by ring.
assert (0 <= m * n - two_p (N + l) * q).
assert (m * n - two_p (N + l) * q < two_p (N + l)).
apply Z.le_lt_trans with (two_p (N + l) * d - two_p l).
apply Zdiv_unique with (m * n - two_p (N + l) * q).
Lemma Zdiv_unique_2: forall x y q, y > 0 -> 0 < y * q - x <= y -> Z.div x y = q - 1.
replace ((q - 1) * y) with (y * q - y) by ring.
Lemma Zdiv_mul_opp: forall m l, l >= 0 -> two_p (N+l) < m * d <= two_p (N+l) + two_p l -> forall n, 0 < n <= two_p N -> Z.div n d = - Z.div (m * (-n)) (two_p (N + l)) - 1.
intros m l l_pos [LO HI] n RANGE.
replace (two_p (N + l) * - q - - (m * n)) with (m * n - two_p (N + l) * q) by ring.
assert ((m * n - two_p (N + l) * q) * d = k * n + two_p (N + l) * r).
assert (two_p (N + l) * r <= two_p (N + l) * d - two_p (N + l)).
replace (two_p (N + l) * d - two_p (N + l)) with (two_p (N + l) * (d - 1)) by ring.
Lemma Zquot_mul: forall m l, l >= 0 -> two_p (N+l) < m * d <= two_p (N+l) + two_p l -> forall n, - two_p N <= n < two_p N -> Z.quot n d = Z.div (m * n) (two_p (N + l)) + (if zlt n 0 then 1 else 0).
replace (- - n) with n by ring.
replace (Z.quot n d) with (- Z.quot (-n) d).

Lemma divs_mul_params_sound: forall d m p, divs_mul_params d = Some(p, m) -> 0 <= m < Int.modulus /\ 0 <= p < 32 /\ forall n, Int.min_signed <= n <= Int.max_signed -> Z.quot n d = Z.div (m * n) (two_p (32 + p)) + (if zlt n 0 then 1 else 0).
unfold divs_mul_params; intros d m' p'.
destruct (find_div_mul_params Int.wordsize (Int.half_modulus - Int.half_modulus mod d - 1) d 32) as [[p m] | ]...
Lemma divu_mul_params_sound: forall d m p, divu_mul_params d = Some(p, m) -> 0 <= m < Int.modulus /\ 0 <= p < 32 /\ forall n, 0 <= n < Int.modulus -> Z.div n d = Z.div (m * n) (two_p (32 + p)).
unfold divu_mul_params; intros d m' p'.
destruct (find_div_mul_params Int.wordsize (Int.modulus - Int.modulus mod d - 1) d 32) as [[p m] | ]...

Lemma divs_mul_shift_gen: forall x y m p, divs_mul_params (Int.signed y) = Some(p, m) -> 0 <= m < Int.modulus /\ 0 <= p < 32 /\ Int.divs x y = Int.add (Int.shr (Int.repr ((Int.signed x * m) / Int.modulus)) (Int.repr p)) (Int.shru x (Int.repr 31)).
generalize (Int.signed_range x); unfold n, Int.max_signed; omega.

Theorem divs_mul_shift_1: forall x y m p, divs_mul_params (Int.signed y) = Some(p, m) -> m < Int.half_modulus -> 0 <= p < 32 /\ Int.divs x y = Int.add (Int.shr (Int.mulhs x (Int.repr m)) (Int.repr p)) (Int.shru x (Int.repr 31)).

Theorem divs_mul_shift_2: forall x y m p, divs_mul_params (Int.signed y) = Some(p, m) -> m >= Int.half_modulus -> 0 <= p < 32 /\ Int.divs x y = Int.add (Int.shr (Int.add (Int.mulhs x (Int.repr m)) x) (Int.repr p)) (Int.shru x (Int.repr 31)).
replace (n * (m - Int.modulus)) with (n * m + (-n) * Int.modulus) by ring.
Theorem divu_mul_shift: forall x y m p, divu_mul_params (Int.unsigned y) = Some(p, m) -> 0 <= p < 32 /\ Int.divu x y = Int.shru (Int.mulhu x (Int.repr m)) (Int.repr p).
cut (0 <= Int.unsigned x * m / Int.modulus < Int.modulus).

destruct (find_div_mul_params Int64.wordsize (Int64.half_modulus - Int64.half_modulus mod d - 1) d 64) as [[p m] | ]...

unfold divlu_mul_params; intros d m' p'.
